---
title: Quick Cheesy Chicken Schnitzel & Gravy with Potato Mash & Steamed Veggies
description: A chicken schnitzel with steamed veggies and a buttery potato mash, there’s only one piece missing to finish this puzzle and
complete the picture - a gravy. It’s a classic addition that always ties everything together. You can’t go wrong!
